CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,FScientists are embarking on a new
OL,7,Fmultimillion-pound study they hope
OL,8,Fwill reveal the workings of the
OL,9,Fcellular "light switches" that are a
OL,10,Fpotential cause of cancer.
OL,12,FResearchers from the University of
OL,13,FDundee will examine the signals that
OL,14,Fdrive cell division ` an essential
OL,15,Fprocess that enables our bodies to
OL,16,Fdevelop, and to repair injuries.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,FThey said it is well known that our
OL,7,Fcells must "switch" signals on or off
OL,8,Fto divide, but that what remains
OL,9,Funclear is why some signals must
OL,10,F"flash" continually on and off for our
OL,11,Fcells to divide properly.
OL,13,FThis flashing can control the way in
OL,14,Fwhich cells behave and, if
OL,15,Fmalfunctioning, could lead to health
OL,16,Fconsequences, including the
OL,17,Fdevelopment of cancer.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@SO]rD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,FThe team said decoding these hidden
OL,7,Fsignals could explain how cells divide
OL,8,Faccurately, how this process goes
OL,9,Fwrong in diseases such as cancer, and
OL,10,Fhow these could potentially be treated
OL,11,Fbetter.
OL,13,FStudy lead Professor Adrian Saurin,
OL,14,Ffrom the university's Faculty of
OL,15,FHealth, said: "Many of the proteins
OL,16,Finside our cells are controlled by
OL,17,Fchemical tags ` phosphates ` which are
OL,18,Feffectively light switches.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,F"They attach to proteins to turn them
OL,7,F'on' and when they detach this turns
OL,8,Fthem 'off' again.
OL,10,F"We know a huge amount about which
OL,11,Fproteins are turned 'on' or 'off' at
OL,12,Fany given time in our cells, but what
OL,13,Fwe don't know is how quickly these
OL,14,Fproteins can 'flash' on and off over
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,F"So we're missing a huge part of the
OL,7,Fpuzzle, because the rate that these
OL,8,Fsignals flash could effectively be a
OL,9,Fform of biological morse code, which
OL,10,Fsends messages to control the
OL,11,Fbehaviour."
OL,13,FThe rapid on-off cycles are known as
OL,14,Fphosphorylation`dephosphorylation
OL,15,F(PdP) dynamics.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,FProf Saurin continued: "We have now
OL,7,Fcreated the first tools to decipher
OL,8,Fthis code, which we hope will explain
OL,9,Fhow our cells divide accurately, and
OL,10,Fshine a light on how this can be used
OL,11,Fto benefit patients affected by
OL,12,Fcancer."
OL,14,FStudy co-investigator Dr Tony Ly, from
OL,15,FDundee University's Faculty of Life
OL,16,FSciences, said: "We're especially
OL,17,Fpleased to be leading this project
OL,18,Ffrom Dundee since protein
OL,19,Fphosphorylation is a topic that Dundee
OL,20,Fis already internationally recognised
OL,21,Ffor.
OL,26,@nD@XOUtD@HO]xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,F"This research capitalises on our
OL,7,Flongstanding collaboration, bringing
OL,8,Ftogether complementary expertise, to
OL,9,Fshed new light on an aspect of
OL,10,Fphosphorylation that is virtually
OL,11,Funexplored.
OL,13,F"Unlocking this knowledge will present
OL,14,Fus with an opportunity to better
OL,15,Funderstand cancer in the future,
OL,16,Fperhaps revealing new treatment ideas."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,FThe eight-year project is funded by a
OL,7,F#4 million award from Wellcome and
OL,8,Fwill be conducted in conjunction with
OL,9,Fthe Max Planck Institute of Molecular
OL,10,FPhysiology in Dortmund, Germany.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777435458
OL,3,CStudy of cellular 'light switches'
OL,4,Ccould spark new cancer treatments
OL,6,FProfessor Andrea Musacchio, director
OL,7,Fat the Max Planck Institute and also a
OL,8,Fco-investigator, said "Our expertise
OL,9,Fin the biochemical reconstitution of
OL,10,Fthe kinetochore complements the
OL,11,Fdiverse skillsets of our team and
OL,12,Fgives us the opportunity to understand
OL,13,Fthese patterns during cell division in
OL,14,Fhealthy cells, and what goes wrong in
OL,15,Fcancer cells that allow them to evolve
OL,16,Fand become resistant to chemotherapy."
OL,26,@pD@WOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
